data.description: Back on the Market as buyer did not perform,Welcome to your new home, updated 3 BR split plan, single level home with Great Room in desirable Sun Groves! New AC and Soft Water system just 2 years ago, granite tops & under-mount kitchen sink & pull out faucet w/ large center Island bar, & stainless appliances! tile floors T/O, carpet in 2 bedrooms! Master BR also has  tile flooring, with luxurious tub & separate shower in bath with new Granite tops & dual sinks, plus walk-in closet! Two Split BRS & bath w/ granite & dual sinks on other side of home are perfect for everyone else! New interior paint & blinds, & exterior recently repainted too! New grass sod & rock in HUGE back yard is ready for your finishing touches. Fantastic schools & parks nearby with shopping & freeways not much further
